          Matic had a poor game today. He was all over the pitch which is the opposite of what you want. He also looked lightweight in a couple of challenges. Chelsea are at home to QPR next week which I can't see going any way other than a huge Chelsea win, so Mikel should play. As for this game, I think Utd deserved a point. Chelsea were slightly better but not 2 points better. I was distinctly un-impressed with Di Maria. A couple of decent moments early on in the 1st half but after that, pretty much every cross he attempted hit a Chelsea player & he didn't make any mazy runs in the 2nd half. You expect a lot more against the top teams for £60m.
